review: It's interesting. Some of it works pretty well, some of it is pretty frustrating and also impossible to navigate: for instance, the language games. They're ALL in Mandarin w/ no option to change this anywhere. My daughter doesn't have any background in Mandarin, and the games require a basic understanding of the language. I may update with more areas that could stand to be improved upon. It's a neat concept. Just wish it was better executed. And, as someone else commented, it is sluggish - even on our fairly decent tablet.
